cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement

Class EntitlementVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.EntitlementVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEntitlementVisitor

    public class EntitlementVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEntitlementVisitor
    Used to aid in building up a printable inventory of the IEntitlementServiceAPI to list out all the cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.Service, Entitlement (which are subclassed as Roles and Permissions), and User. This class is a primary actor in the Visitor pattern usage for building up a printable inventory of Entitlement items.
    See Also:
    cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.Service, Entitlement, Role, Permission, cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement..User

      • visitEntitlement

        public java.lang.String visitEntitlement(Entitlement entitlement)
        Visits an Entitlement object and returns a string representing its properties. For Role objects, will use the RoleIterator to iterate over all the child Roles and Permissions and include them in the returned string.
        Specified by:
        visitEntitlement in interface IEntitlementVisitor
        Parameters:
        entitlement - either a Role or Permission to get the properties for
        Returns:
